snippet.title: Combinations made easy
snippet.description:
Combinations are easy to work out and understand using the right method.  Combinations differ from permutations in that with combinations order does not matter....so take this into account and the answer is easy.
Part of the permutations and combinations playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjbxBzUM6SLnfCY-opFl5WOdRLVzNwyoI To support free math on Patreon (thank you): https://www.patreon.com/tecmath To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
